camps.name: Mount Ulap
camps.description: Mount Ulap is a 1846 meter high mountain located in Itogon, Benguet. It is a popular hiking destination in the Cordilleras because of its beginner-friendly trails and scenic views of the Cordillera mountains.

camps.name: Calagas Islands
camps.description: Calaguas is a group of islands in the Philippine province of Camarines Norte. It includes the major islands of Tinaga Island and Guintinua Island, the minor Maculabo Island, as well as several other minor islands.
